OL,3,CMan seriously injured in suspected hit-
OL,4,Cand-run on New Year's Day
OL,6,FA man has been seriously injured
OL,7,Ffollowing a suspected hit-and-run
OL,8,Fcollision in Northumberland.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police received a report
OL,11,Fof a crash in the area of Marygate, in
OL,12,FBerwick, just before 12:30am on New
OL,13,FYear's Day.
OL,15,FIt was reported that a red Vauxhall
OL,16,FCorsa had left the road and collided
OL,17,Fwith a pedestrian on the path, before
OL,18,Fdriving away from the scene.
