OL,4,Cand-run on New Year's Day
OL,6,FThe pedestrian, a man in his 20s,
OL,7,Fsustained serious injuries and was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital, where he is
OL,9,Fcurrently receiving treatment.
OL,11,FA 24-year-old man has since been
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of causing
OL,13,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,14,FHe remains in police custody while
OL,15,Fenquiries are ongoing.
OL,17,FFollowing the incident, a number of
OL,18,Fenquiries have been carried out by
OL,19,Fofficers from Northumbria Police's
OL,20,FRoads Policing Unit.
